        "swaparoo",
        "brdeployer",
        "brcommittee"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到Core是部署者，Ctee是委员会。在标注上，我打算把Core显示为\"swaparoo<brdeployer\"，Ctee显示为\"swaparoo<brcommittee\"，这样角色更清晰。Zoe保持原名可以吗？另外Voter1简写为V1？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "Zoe",
        "Voter1",
        "V1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，Zoe保持原名，Voter1用V1简写。流程第一步是Core调用Zoe的startInstance，传入FinTech_PaymentGateway参数来启动支付网关实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "startInstance"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一条消息已添加：Core-)Zoe: startInstance(FinTech_PaymentGateway)。接下来呢？",
