    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后Zoe要启动AuthVault，这是通过Ctee来执行的。Zoe发消息给Ctee调用start方法，参数是FinTech_AuthVault。注意这里有个细节——我文档里写的是FinTech_AuthVault}，右括号带了个花括号，可能是笔误，但先按FinTech_AuthVault处理吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe",
