      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Ctee--)Zoe和Zoe--)Core的FinTech_FraudDetection返回。接下来Core要主动调用Ctee的getVoterInvitations方法获取投票邀请，这里涉及FinTech_LedgerService，格式是E(FinTech_LedgerService).getVoterInvitations(FinTech_AuthVault)。",
